des:
My life through a digital assistant enabled journal. I've written journals and blogs sometimes in the past and it never really stuck. This is an easy format for me and I see these digital assistants becoming a huge part of all our lives going forward so it's a great way to connect my past with the future. I'll update frequently so check back to see what's going on in my life and ask me anything so I can update it in the next version.
